[2026-04-13]
CATEGORY: BUILD_BUG
SERVICE: poc
TASK: poc1 iter3 — split boundary detection
SYMPTOM: _split_text_by_starts returned [] despite LLM correctly identifying section
         boundaries. "split FAILED (boundary detection: got 0 slices for N sections)"
ROOT_CAUSE: Two independent LLM copy-paste failure modes for "start" strings:
         1. Whitespace normalisation: source has '1.  **text' (two spaces), LLM
            returns '1. **text' (one space). str.find() is exact-byte — no match.
         2. Markdown stripping: source has '**c. Procedures**', LLM returns
            'c. Procedures' (bold markers dropped). Still no match after whitespace fix.
         Both occur even at temperature=0 and with explicit "copy verbatim" instructions.
PREVENTED_BY: Any verbatim-text boundary matching against LLM output must normalise
              both needle and haystack: strip inline markdown markers (*_`#) AND
              collapse whitespace runs before str.find(). _norm_map() in pageindex.py
              is the reference implementation.
SOLUTION: Updated _norm_map to strip _MARKDOWN_INLINE chars in addition to collapsing
          whitespace; updated _find_norm needle path identically. Both failure modes
          resolved in one pass.
DEAD_ENDS: Whitespace-only fix caught case 1 but not case 2. Needed a second diagnostic
           run (with failure detail logging) to surface the markdown stripping mode.

[2026-04-13]
CATEGORY: INFRA
SERVICE: poc
TASK: poc1 iter3 — build pipeline
SYMPTOM: Build crashes mid-run on large documents (107KB) with ResourceExhausted 429.
         Happens consistently at step 6 or 7.
ROOT_CAUSE: asyncio.gather fires all concurrent LLM calls simultaneously. No backoff.
            Small documents complete before quota window resets; large ones exceed it.
PREVENTED_BY: Any asyncio.gather over LLM calls needs retry+backoff on 429.
              Five attempts at 5s/10s/20s/40s covers typical Vertex quota reset windows.
SOLUTION: Added try/except ResourceExhausted with exponential backoff in _llm_call.
DEAD_ENDS: Manual retries (running build again) failed repeatedly before backoff was added.
